customize_plugin_tips: Customize plugin execution file path and parameters, default execution file path is client plugins directory.
customize_plugin_tips_sip003: Customize SIP003-standard plugin execution file path and parameters, default execution file path is client plugins directory.
only_for_server_groups: Only for the subscription server groups (right click groups on the server list and function menu will pop up)
polling_tips: Select node one by one to send request
random_tips: Select node at random to send request
readme: checkout plugins installation instructions on github readme page
readme_acl: Proxy server will restart when back to main page, checkout acl instructions on github readme page
please_confirm_v2ray-plugin_installed_on: The v2ray-plugin has been built-in, there is nothing to do. If you want to use external v2ray-plugin, put it into client plugins directory or create a soft link to there.
please_confirm_kcptun_installed_on_your_: Must install kcptun first, check more details on github readme page. For Windows/Mac(Intel)/Ubuntu users, after download the plugin, rename it to kcptun and put kcptun into plugins directory. Mac(M1) users need to run command "brew install kcptun" to install plugin and then run "sudo ln -s `which kcptun_client` [plugins directory]/kcptun "to create a soft link to client plugins directory.
not_applicable_to_linux_snap_application: not applicable to linux snap version
recover_pac_file_with_link: Recover the pac file using the gfw-list link below
recover_pac_file_with_file: Recover the pac file using the local gfw-list file
server_url_not_set: Server URL not set, please remove the subscription and add it again.
pac_port_tips: Port where PAC file is served
restart_when_changed: Proxy server will restart when back to main page
restart_pac_tips: PAC server will restart when back to main page, some browsers need to be manually restarted for pac rules to take effect
gfwlist_url_tips: GFWList file used to generate PAC
load_balance_tips: Client will try to connect multiple servers and disperse traffic pressure to each server
plugins_dir_tips: On Windows, some external plugins (such as v2ray-plugin) should be placed at this directory.
import_server_subscription_from_clipboar: Http(s) url that be used to download multi lines of `ss(r)://` text data encoded by base64, the downloaded data will be parsed by client. Tested & Supported service: paofu,monocloud(not all nodes are available),fast-frog(not recommended).
the_recovery_is_failed: The recovery is failed! please confirm whether the file format is json
reset_all_data_tips: This action will reset all data to its defaults.
